tatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/c35ef2ad5b40072f648e11f51ee784e8.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/590a54030fe17daab70d3281d906d072.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >選擇四條道路之一，或根據自身喜好組合它們，解鎖全新能力，克服意想不到的挑戰，並揭開島嶼的最終謎團。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >狩獵之路：適合足智多謀、觀察入微的追蹤者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巨樹之路：適合為了更美好的未來而放棄暴力的和平療癒者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由之路：適合崇尚藝術與外交而非武器之人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >暗夜之路：適合堅定守護島嶼、拒絕將魔法簡單地劃分為光明與黑暗的守護者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/22934531cd82a25617c8c7b33715db31.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/8046177400f2cccef66d4722eff842e5.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不速之客乘飛艇從海上而來，一座神秘的水下城市向遊客敞開大門，一個飽受戰爭蹂躪的精靈部落正在尋找新的領袖——所有這些事件交織在一起，構成了一張不可思議的事件之網。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/1f242d9d23e31264fefebbf87e9f6165.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 動畫激情場景</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 兩種類型的生殖器（毛茸茸和經典）</p><p class=\