steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/49dbc79200da187e3e05489a8bda5b30.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=282 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/e60e4a5f82be10629111fa7ff4ca8ee2.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/0792608924c6a77a190f96593c2faa0e.poster.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=776 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/0792608924c6a77a190f96593c2faa0e.webm?t=1776437664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/0792608924c6a77a190f96593c2faa0e.mp4?t=1776437664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/04a381de1f0a973c1ce4b23b30a83fc3.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The mysterious island of Lyndaria, home to vastly different tribes, has survived wars, cataclysms, and the fall of gods. Now its inhabitants must face a sudden, unforeseen threat, with Maya once again at the center of it all - a naive, deeply romantic explorer with a naive, sweet nature and the body of a porn star.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/c35ef2ad5b40072f648e11f51ee784e8.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/590a54030fe17daab70d3281d906d072.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Follow one of four Paths or combine them as you see fit to unlock new abilities, overcome unexpected challenges, and unravel the island’s final mystery.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The Path of the Hunt. For cunning and observant trackers who notice every detail.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The Path of the Great Tree. For peaceful healers who have forsaken violence for the greater good.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The Path of Freedom. For those who favor art and diplomacy over weapons.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>The Path of the Night. For unwavering defenders of the island who refuse to divide magic into light and dark.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/22934531cd82a25617c8c7b33715db31.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/8046177400f2cccef66d4722eff842e5.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=503 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Uninvited guests arrive by airship from across the sea, a mysterious underwater city opens its gates to visitors, and a war-torn tribe of alfins searches for a new leaderб all weaving together into an incredible web of events.</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/1f242d9d23e31264fefebbf87e9f6165.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 Animated hot scenes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴Two types of genitalia (furry and classic)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 Art hand-drawn by our talented artists</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 Various mini-games</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 Character progression throughout the game, influenced by your choices</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 Event and gift system</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴Multiple endings</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 A wardrobe of sexy outfits for the main heroine</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 Day and night cycle</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 Plenty of side quests to complement the main storyline</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 Interactive locations where you can collect items</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 Rituals (potion-making)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 A sequential map navigation system where all sorts of unexpected events can occur along the way</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌴 Variability not only in the game’s ending but also throughout the quests</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/2b32e46cea0d2b7e4b3d6bc11a195f99.avif?t=1776437664\" width=780 height=67 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4605070/extras/e4cd8d371998c959509be2103dd49e